attributes.Long form description: The student is to assemble the rolling cart. The student first attaches the bar legs and then uses the screwdriver to tighten the screws on the bar legs. Second, the student attaches and screws the bar legs and the base frame together. Then, the student attaches the bracket on both sides of the bottom tray and places a hex nut and hexagon cap nut. Next, the student slides the middle tray and the top tray down. Then, the student lays the rolling cart down on the table. Next, the student assembles the top tray and then the middle tray. The student ensures the hexagon cap nut is tighten. Next, the student attaches all four wheels of the rolling cart. Lastly, the student stands the rolling cart on the table.
